<h2>Common Ways to Manipulate the View in Jmol </h2>
</div>
Below are descriptions of how to do some common things with the Jmol
view: <a href="#zoom">Zoom</a> | <a href="#rotate_">Rotate</a> | <a href="#spin_">Set
Spinning</a> | <a href="#atom_size">Change Atom Size</a>
| <a href="#bond_size">Change Bond Size</a> | <a href="#measure">Make
and
Show Measurements</a> | <a href="#cartoon">Make
Cartoon Views of Biomolecules</a>.
</div>
