<td>
<p style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">Making
and Displaying Measurements</p>
<div id="divEthane_for_measurements">
<div id="tableEthane_for_measurements" class="floatLeftDiv">
<table style="text-align: left; width: 300px;" border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2">
