<td style="vertical-align: top;"> Figure
4:&nbsp; View of staggered ethane ( <a href="../ethane-staggered-3-21G.log">ethane-staggered-3-21G.log</a>)
to practice making measurements on. &nbsp;To make live click
on the
link in the image. &nbsp;C-H bond lengths 0.108 nm, H&#8211;C&#8211;H angle
108.1 degrees, H&#8211;C&#8211;C&#8211;H dihedral angle 60.0 degrees.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
